strings: <voice_0x01001CEB><se_high>media princess: When they first met you, I didn't know what to do
<voice_0x01001CEC><se_high>media princess: I and my father decided to travel alone.
<voice_0x01001CED><se_high>media princess: But he keeps talking about you. <hero> It's yours.
<voice_0x01001CEF><se_high>media princess: Maybe! When Prince Charming loves you the most <hero>
